summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2017 JEEP CHEROKEE. WHILE DRIVING APPROXIMATELY 45 MPH, THE SERVICE SHIFTER WARNING INDICATOR AND SEVERAL OTHER WARNING INDICATORS ILLUMINATED. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO CLINTON AUTO GROUP (2850 VALLEY WEST DRIVE, CLINTON, IA 52732) FOR DIAGNOSTIC TESTING. THE CONTACT WAS NOT ADVISED AS TO WHAT NEEDED TO BE REPAIRED OR REPLACED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE VIN WAS UNKNOWN. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 10,175.
